data.description: ONE YEAR HOME WARRANTY INCLUDED. NEW CENTRAL AIR CONDITIONING WILL BE INSTALLED PRIOR TO CLOSING. Don't miss the chance to make Clarence your new home. Step inside and you'll first notice the open concept kitchen space. This home also offers the convenience of main floor laundry, making daily chores a breeze. In the spacious bathroom you'll find a delightful surprise - a heated floor that pampers you with warmth and comfort, elevating your morning routine. Situated on a large lot, the outdoor space of this property offers endless possibilities. Whether you envision a lush garden or a spacious play area this could be the perfect property for you!
